column1: Baby Barnaby's////Amazing breakfast place and for the price it's outrageously good. The parking situation is a bit complicated but worth it. The french toast is great
column2: it does come with cinnamon so if you're not a fan of it just ask without it. The potatoes come in great quantity and trust me
column3: you'll be glad it does. We didn't wait too long and they were super nice. Loved the place definitely going back.
